Assistant Manager Logistics, Karachi, Pakistan
KMLG Cement
-
Karachi
We are looking for a self motivated, dynamic & result oriented individual. CVs are invited for following position, based at Maple Leaf Cement Factory Limited, Karachi Office.
Assistant Manager Logistics
Location - Regional Office Karachi
Requisite Qualification & Experience:
- MBA from HEC/PEC recognized Institution
- 1-3 Years of experience
Key Responsibilities:
- Management of inbound & Outbound Logistics (Expertise in coal management will be preferred)
- Warehouse management
- Liaison with port authorities
- Responsible for transport arrangements (arranging transport for order deliveries)
We offer an attractive salary package commensurate with excellent learning & development opportunities.
